     H            Y.
      ** AB#RFW **********************************************
      *  CHECK UPDATE DATE OF EDI862FD AND SYSTEM DATE       *
      *  N.HYOTO 2001.06.25
      ********************************* AB#RFV ***************
     FABFZP01 IF  E                    DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  120WK
     I                                        7  12 WKDATE
     C* ERROR FLAG
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           FLAG    1
     C*
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLAG
     C                     TIME           WK
     C*
     C                     READ QWHFDBAS                 90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '1'       FLAG
     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C           ATRDAT    IFNE WKDATE
     C                     MOVE '1'       FLAG
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
